This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the arXiv sub-category of Computer Science - Computation and Language (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves the use of neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
